# CSS Standards

## Core Principles
- Use CSS custom properties (`--color-primary`, `--spacing-unit`).
- Apply BEM (`block__element--modifier`) for naming.
- Implement a mobile-first design approach.

## Best Practices
- Use `grid`, `flexbox`, and `clamp()` for layout.
- Avoid inline styles unless absolutely necessary.
- Alphabetize CSS declarations.
- Optimize styles by avoiding overly specific selectors.

